<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Birthday Indah Nauli Damanik</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Abu-abu sangat muda/bersih */
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #2d3436;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #636e72;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #2d3436; /* Warna gelap minimalis */
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #000;
        }

        /* Animasi sederhana untuk teks */
        .fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card fade-in">
        <h1>Happy Birthday, <br> Indah Nauli Damanik</h1>
        <p>A special day for a special person. Semoga hari ini penuh dengan kebahagiaan dan kesuksesan.</p>
        
        <button class="btn" onclick="celebrate()">Klik untuk Kejutan</button>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.5.1/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        function celebrate() {
            confetti({
                particleCount: 150,
                spread: 70,
                origin: { y: 0.6 },
                colors: ['#2d3436', '#dfe6e9', '#636e72'] // Warna minimalis
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
